ygData.messageBody:
You mean, the "working as intended per the sock puppet" song.
Actually, this is kinda funny. But, you have to admit our songs do
have funny names. Haven't you ever listened to the radio and someone
will call in and say play that one song by Soandso. DJ says, "sing
it." Hey! Now that's an idea! Next time they say "play mana song,"
tell them to say the name of the song or try singing it themselves
first, LOL! :p

~Beatdrop
